{"type": "article", "id": 9780, "title": "Italic Light 意大利灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-20T07:12:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235423gUsklTqemhrdY3X0.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这款意大利灯由 COORDINATION-berlin 在 2015 年米兰设计周期间展出，灯的外部是一个大理石外壳，光束透过大理石内部放射出来，内置的是一个 LED 循环灯环，一个内置转换器和一个纺织电缆。灯具遵循极简主义设计风格，大理石的白和蓝色的配色看上简单优雅。这是 <a href=\"http://www.coordination-berlin.com/?lang=en\" target=\"_blank\">COORDINATION-berlin 的官方主页</a>，感兴趣的话可以查看他们更多信息。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235421ftB5TQ6R0AKFchHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.9193154\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354218zWjQJk5vhb3tPUZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235421RSnz3G5CeZrigjPD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.3997555\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235422E24bJFgMy1Ga7Omu.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.12224939\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235422B0xmR4qU3d1ErQeD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.09046455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}